Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:05.30,Asteroid - Book1,,0,0,0,,{\org(586,449)\frz15.99\pos(538,437)}生日石
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:05.30,Asteroid - Book2,,0,0,0,,{\org(654,656)\frz15.99\pos(606,632)}欣赏天然石的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:12:59.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,生日石
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.07,0:13:03.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,要是按顺序介绍的话就能写十二回了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:05.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,太天真了  梦露
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:11.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,也有按每天算的生日石  竟然能写366回连载文章
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:13.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,学姐好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.57,0:13:15.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,看来留级兴致勃勃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:20.90,Asteroid - HandWrite,,0,0,0,,{\fs80\pos(744,557)\frz15.66\c&H9E959D&}主题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:18.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,大家都确定了主题  好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.85,0:13:20.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈不是要写小行星吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.27,0:13:23.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,虽然是这样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:26.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,要是有人看了我的文章产生了兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:29.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,比我们先找到了小行星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:31.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好痛苦  好不甘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:34.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我想应该没事的  毕竟这事比较硬核
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:37.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,总之主题是决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.85,0:13:39.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈  那是作业吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:43.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不是  是社团活动用的文章
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:44.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,行文会不会怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.77,0:13:47.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:50.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:54.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,抱歉  太过于说明和解释了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:57.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真是的  就是科普文章  这没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.05,0:13:59.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,也不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.80,0:14:01.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,文章太过于普通了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:03.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,让读者无法感觉到米菈你的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:09.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我们学生会的会刊  也会在文笔和表达方式上好好斟酌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:16.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,就算你对我说这么多  我也不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:16.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.75,0:14:27.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这是米菈不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:30.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,向别人听取意见自己却中途逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.02,0:14:35.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,人家这么努力的成果就这样被否定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:38.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,也不是不能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:42.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米莎姐虽然当学生会长时做事很严格
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:45.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不过却意外地不太会说话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:49.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但多亏这个  我和米莎姐的聊天终于有进展了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:51.87,Asteroid - Chat,,0,0,0,,{\frz7.001\move(1142,328,1212,452,26,4989)}要怎么做才会原谅我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:51.87,Asteroid - Chat,,0,0,0,,{\frz7.001\move(1050,178,1114,302,0,4989)}让米菈不开心了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:51.87,Asteroid - Chat,,0,0,0,,{\frz7.352\move(1242,634,1312,750,0,4989)}那可真是不妙啊  米菈说了些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:52.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,简直是天上掉馅饼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:54.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小铃  你都说出声了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:54.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.42,0:14:58.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,原以为会很顺利的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.07,0:15:01.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,大家最初不都这样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:04.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我第一次做的面包就没有被采用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.65,0:15:06.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是不好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:10.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不是  说是太没品了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:12.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是胖次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.45,0:15:17.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是蓝发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.57,0:15:21.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,说是在找用在文章上的图片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:22.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:25.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,就当是转换心情  米菈来画怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:27.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,以前不是挺喜欢画画吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.52,0:15:31.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,说是要用于介绍木星和它的卫星  类似希腊神话的画
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.77,0:15:33.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:35.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,希腊神话？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:39.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,希腊神话和星星之间有着很多联系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:42.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好像很有趣  我也读读看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:43.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.72,0:15:44.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:46.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,发送
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:51.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,如果报道也像这样刷刷地写完就轻松了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.45,0:15:54.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.42,0:16:00.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈帮我画了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.30,0:16:02.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.22,0:16:06.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  特别可爱的插图
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:07.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:08.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,多亏你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:09.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,0:16:10.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:15.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈选了漫画的形式啊
